tegien liefert sie neue Lösungsansätze.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Apr 2022) 4aDigitale Medien. 4aGesellschaft. 4aInvisible Hand. 4aKommunikation. 4aKrise. 4aKrisenkommunikation. 4aMedien. 4aMediensoziologie. 4aMedienwissenschaft. 4aNetzwerk. 4aSocial Media. 4aWeb 2.0. 4aWirtschaft. 4aWirtschaftswissenschaft. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Media Studies.2bisacsh  aCommunication.  aCrisis.  aDigital Media.  aEconomics.  aEconomy.  aInvisible Hand.  aMedia Studies.  aMedia.  aNetwork.  aSocial Media.  aSociety.  aSociology of Media.  aWeb 2.0.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2021 Part 2z978311074335708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Sociology 2021z9783110753967oZDB-23-DSL40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978383945954640uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839459546423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839459546/original  a978-3-11-074335-7  DG Plus PP Package 2021 Part 2b2021  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DSLb2021